name: Scary Tsundere
description:
Class: Tsundere
Personality: She might be cranky, but she just wanna be friends!
Type: I declare this girl is... SCARY

"Cute or Scary Series"
You know those alien girls. When you look at them you often
think - is she cute... or scary?! So, let's decide then! Each week we drop two types of cards with alien girls. By buying one you vote on them being Cute or Scary!
